{"tid":1089340,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"聽到啲人話支持嗰啲中游球隊 真係笑而不語.......","createTime":"2019-04-02T17:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T10:23:36.000Z","uid":218922,"like":18,"dislike":110,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"42ac57dcc7ba770b345ad55156911306c39324fb","tid":1089340,"uid":218922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:12:55.000Z","msg":"正正常常支持吓啲勁旅爭標分子咪算囉<br />\n有啲人總係要令到自己好與眾不同咁<br />\n支持埋啲廢隊以為自己好特別<br />\n鍾意埋啲咩修咸頓愛華頓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺波台見到依啲隊都有post就想笑<br />\n高不成低不就有咩好討論？<br />\n就算係李斯特城依啲曇花一現嘅咪又係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發現總係有啲球迷以為自己好清高<br />\n懶係支持埋啲小眾球隊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然熱狗痢狗依兩隊都係廢<br />\n一隊冇攞過英超一隊冇歷史冇冠軍<br />\n不過都總好過啲人話支持屈福特般尼矛夫嗰啲囉<br />\n<br />\n利伸：鏝"},{"pid":"cf75cd7895d6584337d4717f019dc8c5228f00c2","tid":1089340,"uid":37618,"like":50,"dislike":4,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:14:18.000Z","msg":"支持咩隊關你撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戇撚鳩鳩"},{"pid":"fa2f9210df22393766b8a6f3b9742cbc5d34ec2e","tid":1089340,"uid":218922,"like":1,"dislike":27,"score":-26,"quote":{"pid":"cf75cd7895d6584337d4717f019dc8c5228f00c2","tid":1089340,"uid":37618,"like":50,"dislike":4,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:14:18.000Z","msg":"支持咩隊關你撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戇撚鳩鳩"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:16:48.000Z","msg":"可唔可以解釋俾我聽點解垃圾都有人支持？？"},{"pid":"e118a37bdcc07e1a21284aef6411741a330d6ffc","tid":1089340,"uid":202348,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"ci